{"tid":473802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實iq 唔重要，最重要一定係熱情，意志，心態一","createTime":"2017-11-19T14:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T10:43:58.000Z","uid":123335,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"758c609e23bf9091e9b14fe88fa22a991484616d","tid":473802,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"IQ好換句話姐係邏輯能力高<br />\n個人思考會好理性 好make sense <br />\n<br />\n但其實iq高唔重要<br />\n世界上高成就既人, iq唔一定高, 但一定係有熱情<br />\n例如你對個世界冇熱情，用冷淡灰暗既眼光去睇世界，你個人會頹，會冇動力，冇乜特別目標，人生冇咩追求，覺得人生冇咩值得感動，街都唔多想出，唔會特別想見人，唔會想花心機追女，唔會keep住去留意世界有咩最新最潮既野...etc <br />\n又或者會, 頹下頹下 彎住個腰骨咁上連登9 hea 時間, 然後用logic去judge d post , 將iq用係駁人嘴方面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知好多連登巴打都高iq <br />\n可惜, Iq, logical skill只不過係工具<br />\n如果你對人生冇熱情，冇目標<br />\nIq200都係得物無所用"},{"pid":"776e04042527fbb18d1ae6e37b5fb4387c1eb115","tid":473802,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"Bros how see<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fb301b65591463abce2b9cf4b91f39db824b83","tid":473802,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"Iq高係bonus <br />\n但如果對生活無左目標 熱情 你咁聰明都無意思"},{"pid":"7165c318abe24069a7d9c524b8d090953c04c34a","tid":473802,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:45:38.000Z","msg":"乜Q"},{"pid":"92c93c0117edd2bf4b57ac04a79b25b4f19d47dd","tid":473802,"uid":12058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb716e1f5b5bdbf53be5ac3adbc40a08d65ce772","tid":473802,"uid":21483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"幾樣都重要，唔好又扮看破世事撚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d4d4d535eb2d67e70d634ff835fe435e723a7c","tid":473802,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"熱情冇問題, 但唔好太過樂觀<br />\n係戰場上因為樂觀既人冇危機意識<br />\n往往係最快死既人"},{"pid":"95d02134f16f97d2c1e90c0a54199a356141d24c","tid":473802,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n個人有正確目標做野都精神啲"},{"pid":"04b0515530fd8e539ffa2a398e42c2a59ec16f06","tid":473802,"uid":33825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442d1fae87a4884c31085c8c55319dcc87ad0e3a","tid":473802,"uid":68864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"iq 100 有熱情<br />\n長期用100%力 只係做到50分嘅嘢。<br />\niq 200 間唔中心血來潮<br />\n用兩吓腦做到100分嘅嘢"},{"pid":"e4f236267d3e4b17fb3ed988a37468a7b7fa0ebb","tid":473802,"uid":59705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4837240550977f99a211d98c7506c2618b204353","tid":473802,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"樣衰好難有熱情"},{"pid":"d69c56353bc1a0a43866f5f2e4ab31fcf884baaa","tid":473802,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:45:38.000Z","msg":"世界放棄了我，因此我放棄世界"},{"pid":"4f0b1ff52d1ff7d25a176964bc494725cf797d69","tid":473802,"uid":131962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"Agger"}]}